      "role": "user",
      "content": "i'll try tracemalloc. one thing though, when these spikes happen, it's almost like the memory just vanishes into thin air. i'll be looking at the monitor and and suddenly a huge chunk of RAM is just gone. is there any way to see if a specific process or some hidden background task is \"stealing\" the memory from my main script?",
